%% Diagram: Railway Oriented Programming
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    A["op1<br/>Result&lt;A, E&gt;"] -->|Ok| B["op2<br/>Result&lt;B, E&gt;"]
    B -->|Ok| C["op3<br/>Result&lt;C, E&gt;"]
    C -->|Ok| OK["Final Ok"]

    A -.->|Err| ERR["Final Err<br/>(short-circuit)"]
    B -.->|Err| ERR
    C -.->|Err| ERR
